column2: SELECT up_id,  dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) as SpecobjId   FROM #upload  WHERE  dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) IS NOT NULL  SELECT TOP #   s.ra,s.dec,s.plate,s.mjd,s.fiberid,s.z,s.zErr,s.zWarning,s.class,s.dec,s.fiberID,cast(str(s.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,s.snMedian,s.sourceType,s.specObjID,s.subClass,s.velDisp,p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj,cast(str(p.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec,p.r,p.fiberFlux_z,p.modelFlux_z,p.petroR5#_r,p.petroR9#_r  FROM ..SpecObj as s  JOIN ..PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  JOIN #x AS x ON x.SpecobjID=s.SpecobjID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  s.zWarning = # AND ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
